Class ThresholdNode<T extends Comparable<T>>

java.lang.Object
  edu.nd.darts.cimon.ThresholdNode<T>

public class ThresholdNode<T extends Comparable<T>>
extends Object

Node which holds condition monitoring requests for event monitors. These nodes maintain the threshold value that will trigger a state change for the condition, and a link to the ConditionNode which should be notified.

Constructor Detail

ThresholdNode

public ThresholdNode(int monitorId,
                     T threshold,
                     long period,
                     ExpressionNode node)
Node which holds condition monitoring requests for event monitors. These nodes maintain the threshold value that will trigger a state change for the condition, and a link to the ConditionNode which should be notified.

Parameters:
monitorId - unique id of monitor
threshold - threshold value for monitored condition. Notification to condition node will be triggered when current value surpasses threshold
period - maximum allowed period (in milliseconds) for monitoring of this condition
node - link to ConditionNode which registered this condition monitor
